Options and plugin collections from my VIM in OpenSuSe

Add the follow ine at the end of /etc/vimrc file

" Load user vim configuration file if exists
if filereadable($HOME . "/.vim/vimrc.local")
      exec "source " . $HOME . "/.vim/vimrc.local"
endif


Move all files and flders to $HOME/.vim folder.
e.g.
~/.vim/doc
~/.vim/ftplugin
~/.vim/nerdtree_plugin
~/.vim/plugin
~/.vim/syntax
~/.vim/vimrc.local
.....
